creator: Kingswood United Methodist Church
descriptionHtml:
Kingswood United Methodist Church seeks to LOVE God, SERVE others, and BUILD sacred community. This app will help you stay connected with the day-to-day life of Kingswood church. With this app you can:
- Watch or listen to services
- Stay up to date with events and other opportunities with push notifications
- Share your favorite messages via Twitter, Facebook, or email
- Download messages for offline listening
- And so much more!
descriptionShort: Connect with Kingswood United Methodist Church

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: If enabled, the app will show the viewer a prompt to take an action at a designated time during a live stream.
